# Executive Summary - Receipt Organizer PRD

## Vision
Build a mobile-first receipt management system that eliminates the pain of receipt organization for small business owners and contractors.

## Problem Statement
Small business owners waste hours organizing paper receipts for bookkeeping and tax purposes. Current solutions are either too complex or don't integrate well with accounting software.

## Solution
A simple, fast mobile app that:
- Captures receipts in under 5 seconds
- Automatically extracts key data with OCR
- Exports to QuickBooks/Xero formats
- Works offline with cloud sync

## Success Metrics
- Capture-to-export time < 10 minutes for 300 receipts
- OCR accuracy > 95% for merchant, date, amount
- User satisfaction score > 4.5/5.0
